<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>Climate Solutions</title>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    </head>

<body class="bg-base-100">
    <%- include('partials/navbar', { page: '/' }) %>


    <div class="container mx-auto p-4 py-8">
        <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-lg mb-8">
            <div class="hero-content text-center">
                <div class="max-w-md">
                    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Climate Solutions</h1>
                    <p class="py-6">Explore these projects and learn how small actions can make a big difference.</p>
                    <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary <%= page == '/solutions/projects' ? 'active' : '' %>">View Projects</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
            
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_farmlandrestoration01.jpg" alt="Abandoned Farmland Restoration" class="object-cover h-48 w-full rounded-t-xl" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Abandoned Farmland Restoration</h2>
                    <p>Restoring abandoned farmland helps capture carbon, supports wildlife, and makes the soil healthier.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/1" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_alternativecement02.jpg" alt="Alternative Cement" class="object-cover h-48 w-full rounded-t-xl" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Alternative Cement</h2>
                    <p>Making cement in a new way can help lower the amount of carbon it releases by millions of metric tons each year.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/2" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_bicycle_infrastructure.jpg" alt="Bicycle Infrastructure" class="object-cover h-48 w-full rounded-t-xl" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Bicycle Infrastructure</h2>
                    <p>Building bike lanes helps people ride safely and reduces the need to drive cars that cause pollution.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/3" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>